### ‚öñÔ∏è **The Legal Insurance Gap**

Unlike health insurance, **legal insurance** is:

- Rarely employer-sponsored

- Often misunderstood

- Almost never accessible to low-income individuals

Even though some providers like **LegalShield**, **ARAG**, or **LegalZoom** offer prepaid legal plans, they‚Äôre typically geared toward middle-class consumers and small businesses‚Äînot the truly disadvantaged [A](https://www.benzinga.com/money/legal-insurance?copilot_analytics_&citationMarker=9F742443-6C92-4C44-BF58-8F5A7C53B6F1).

