### üß© **What Exists Today**

There *are* some resources, but they‚Äôre fragmented:

- **Legal Aid**: Government-funded, but under-resourced and limited in scope [B](https://www.lawworks.org.uk/legal-advice-individuals?copilot_analytics_%3D&citationMarker=9F742443-6C92-4C44-BF58-8F5A7C53B6F1)

- **LawWorks Clinics**: Free advice for those not eligible for legal aid [B](https://www.lawworks.org.uk/legal-advice-individuals?copilot_analytics_%3D&citationMarker=9F742443-6C92-4C44-BF58-8F5A7C53B6F1)

