- **Employer-sponsored legal plans**: Helpful, but irrelevant if you're unemployed or working low-wage jobs [C](https://lydagroup.com/blog/the-rise-of-legal-insurance-plans-and-how-you-can-use-them-to-your-advantage/?copilot_analytics_%3D&citationMarker=9F742443-6C92-4C44-BF58-8F5A7C53B6F1)

